{"tid":52693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解款車馬路跌錢事件","createTime":"2016-12-24T08:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T10:10:36.000Z","uid":3486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4abccc9d3af7dc62198cdc60628373424c9d8085","tid":52693,"uid":3486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T08:47:04.000Z","msg":"「解款車馬路跌錢事件」，又稱「瘋狂執錢事件」，發生於2014年12月24日，一輛解款車押運約兩億元巨款途經灣仔告士打道時，三個共載有約5,250萬元的膠錢箱跌出車外，其中兩個錢箱封條爆開，鈔票在馬路四散，數十名途人及駕駛人士於馬路共拾去約1,500萬。[2]事後更有人於社交網絡炫耀，引起網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n事後警方呼籲執錢市民自行交出款項，但仍有大批鈔票不知所終，及後警方亦展開拘捕行動。至2015年2月中，警方共拘捕八人，其中兩人提堂後均被判盜竊罪成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E8%A7%A3%E6%AC%BE%E8%BB%8A%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E8%B7%8C%E9%8C%A2%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25B7%258C%25E9%258C%25A2%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=aeR6LJvgMoWyvzS47HCOyWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=97fbfbe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/%E8%A7%A3%E6%AC%BE%E8%BB%8A%E9%A6%AC%E8%B7%AF%E8%B7%8C%E9%8C%A2%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"6788f0919c36e05529ddaae32e01dd05b80a3f5d","tid":52693,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"搵得返晒啲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057f952de2d51c8b3b6480a34199b82b058ea3ec","tid":52693,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵得返晒啲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去曬支那了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81797cb57519a906633bc6198ec0ab4a80203835","tid":52693,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵得返晒啲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去曬支那了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n旅行車經過說法係條「目擊證人」講大話<br />\n沉得住氣果班袋袋平安"}]}